sg":"認同樓主<br />\n人愈大就知世間陰惡<br />\n有d野就愈黎愈保守<br />\n<br />\n表面就有幾單捐贈係你情我願<br />\n另一方面強摘器官、黑市器官就冇停過"},{"pid":"7c7f804fad67807c8dc18c65def000378e0927dd","tid":208991,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:10:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5982ded519458d18b5bb8f6f1bcf5946460519f8","tid":208991,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"又係你條垃圾五毛 快啲死撚開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d083781c00e1d7d03f4ab11b0addc3b2dc8068f3","tid":208991,"uid":80777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"強制死後器官捐贈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1b4cf64f1ad1b03409db818e6ca96ad4057181","tid":208991,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170420/photo/bkn-20170420115552438-0420_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170420115949\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170420%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170420115552438-0420_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170420115949&h=81d343a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧桂思早前已進行過兩次手術。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n26歲鄭凱甄上周四(13日)捐出三分之二肝臟，拯救43歲好媽媽鄧桂思，手術完成至今1周，換肝後的鄧桂思目前情況仍危殆，繼續留醫瑪麗醫院深切治療部。據了解，鄧桂思早前的活肝移植手術有少少失敗，需要再次換肝，是次會進行屍肝移植。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"258fd7aae17abd77b9ad84d341df355812d729a4","tid":208991,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T21:22:30.000Z","msg":"呢單野要講有排講 笑死 失敗埋 轉個撚頭 又有屍肝移植咁抵死都有個wor哈 咁得意 咁有趣 試左活體再試屍肝 哈 冇得頂 定係因為大愛有加乘所以插隊？ 哈有趣"},{"pid":"f461171d9f4002fb8933664a270e39155bc9e714","tid":208991,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/22/075029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg